  <brief_title>Tracking Inflammatory Cells Using Superparamagnetic Particles of Iron Oxide (SPIO) and Magnetic Resonance Imaging (MRI)</brief_title>
  <official_title>In Vivo Tracking of Magnetically-labelled Human Mononuclear Cells Using MRI Scanning</official_title>
